  "className": "qx.ui.container.Resizer",
  "jsdoc": {
    "raw": [
      "*",
      " * The Resizer is a resizable container widget.",
      " *",
      " * It allows to be resized (not moved), normally in",
      " * the right and/or bottom directions. It is an alternative to splitters.",
      " *",
      " * *Example*",
      " *",
      " * Here is a little example of how to use the widget.",
      " *",
      " * <pre class='javascript'>",
      " *   var resizer = new qx.ui.container.Resizer().set({",
      " *     width: 200,",
      " *     height: 100",
      " *   });",
      " *",
      " *   resizer.setLayout(new qx.ui.layout.Canvas());",
      " *   var text = new qx.ui.form.TextArea(\"Resize me\\nI'm resizable\");",
      " *   resizer.add(text, {edge: 0});",
      " *",
      " *   this.getRoot().add(resizer);",
      " * </pre>",
      " *",
      " * This example creates a resizer, configures it with a canvas layout and",
      " * adds a text area to it.",
      " *",
      " * *External Documentation*",
      " *",
      " * <a href='http://qooxdoo.org/docs/#desktop/widget/resizer.md' target='_blank'>",
      " * Documentation of this widget in the qooxdoo manual.</a>",
      " "
    ],
    "@description": [
      {
        "name": "@description",
        "body": "<p>The Resizer is a resizable container widget.\n It allows to be resized (not moved), normally in\n the right and/or bottom directions. It is an alternative to splitters.\n<em>Example</em>\n Here is a little example of how to use the widget.\n </p>\n<pre class='javascript'>\n   var resizer = new qx.ui.container.Resizer().set({\n     width: 200,\n     height: 100\n   });\n   resizer.setLayout(new qx.ui.layout.Canvas());\n   var text = new qx.ui.form.TextArea(\"Resize me\\nI'm resizable\");\n   resizer.add(text, {edge: 0});\n   this.getRoot().add(resizer);\n </pre>\n<p>This example creates a resizer, configures it with a canvas layout and\n adds a text area to it.\n<em>External Documentation</em>\n <a href='http://qooxdoo.org/docs/#desktop/widget/resizer.md' target='_blank'>\n Documentation of this widget in the qooxdoo manual.</a></p>"
      }
